room_title: Escape room "High Limit Hostage" by A2Z Escape in Hays
room_description: Mary Scarbrough seemed like an average, small-town gal until she found herself at High Limit Casino in Las Vegas. What started as a night on the town ended up with a missing person report and possible hostage situation...or worse. Use your detective skills to discover what really happened that night at High Limit Casino before it is too late!
